
<h3>Quizzes:</h3>
All quizzes are now open an available to take.
Here is what you need to do.
<ol>
    <li>
        Log in.
        If you forgot your passcode and/or username,
        email me and I can send it to you.
    </li>
    <li>
        After you log in, on the home screen should display
        current scores. Click on each unit,
        and it will tell you what
